Forward and reverse primers were designed using Primer3 software, version 4.0 (http://frodo.wi.mit.edu/primer3/) to amplify a 164-nt fragment of the 5′UTR conserved region of all aligned pestiviruses. Three specific probes to detect BVDV-1, BVDV-2 and HoBi-like pestivirus were designed using Beacon Designer Software, version 2.06 (Premier Biosoft International, Palo Alto, CA, USA) (Fig. 1
). Primers and probes were synthesised by Eurofins Genomics and are reported in Table 1
.
